{"html":"<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1080px;height:1350px;background:#0D0D0D;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif}.yellow-bar{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:10px;background:#F4C000}.bg-number{position:absolute;right:-30px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-60%);font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:420px;color:rgba(244,192,0,0.04);line-height:1}.glow{position:absolute;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(244,192,0,0.10) 0%,transparent 70%);top:100px;left:200px}.dust{position:absolute;width:6px;height:6px;background:rgba(244,192,0,0.4);border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(244,192,0,0.5)}.main{position:relative;z-index:3;padding:120px 80px 80px 100px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.step-tag{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:48px}.step-num{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:80px;color:#F4C000;line-height:1}.step-label{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}.step-word{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}.step-name{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.headline{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:96px;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.0;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:40px}.headline .accent{color:#F4C000}.divider{width:60px;height:4px;background:#F4C000;margin-bottom:40px}.body-text{font-size:26px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.7;max-width:820px;margin-bottom:40px}.body-text strong{color:#F4C000;font-weight:600}.fact-box{background:rgba(244,192,0,0.06);border-left:4px solid #F4C000;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:36px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px}.fact-stat{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:90px;color:#F4C000;line-height:1}.fact-text{font-size:20px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.5}.detail-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}.detail-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}.detail-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#F4C000;flex-shrink:0}.detail-text{font-size:22px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-weight:300}.detail-text strong{color:#F4C000;font-weight:600}.logo{position:absolute;bottom:56px;right:72px;width:64px;opacity:0.5;z-index:4}.step-indicator{position:absolute;bottom:60px;left:100px;display:flex;gap:8px;z-index:4}.dot{width:28px;height:4px;background:#F4C000;border-radius:2px}.dot-inactive{width:12px;height:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"yellow-bar\"></div><div class=\"bg-number\">03</div><div class=\"glow\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:10%;left:20%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:18%;left:65%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:25%;left:40%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:35%;left:85%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:50%;left:15%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:60%;left:75%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:75%;left:50%\"></div><div class=\"dust\" style=\"top:85%;left:30%\"></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"step-tag\"><div class=\"step-num\">03</div><div class=\"step-label\"><span class=\"step-word\">Efecto</span><span class=\"step-name\">Polvo interno</span></div></div><div class=\"headline\">El calor<br>atrae al<br><span class=\"accent\">polvo.</span></div><div class=\"divider\"></div><div class=\"body-text\">Cuanto m&aacute;s giran los coolers, m&aacute;s polvo aspiran. Se acumula en el <strong>disipador</strong> y act&uacute;a como una manta t&eacute;rmica: el calor ya no puede salir.</div><div class=\"fact-box\"><div class=\"fact-stat\">+15&deg;</div><div class=\"fact-text\">de temperatura promedio<br>en PCs con m&aacute;s de <strong>1 a&ntilde;o</strong> sin limpieza interna profunda.</div></div><div class=\"detail-list\"><div class=\"detail-item\"><div class=\"detail-dot\"></div><span class=\"detail-text\">El polvo bloquea las <strong>aletas del cooler</strong></span></div><div class=\"detail-item\"><div class=\"detail-dot\"></div><span class=\"detail-text\">La pasta t&eacute;rmica se seca y pierde efectividad</span></div></div></div><img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\" /><div class=\"step-indicator\"><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div></div></div>","notes":"Slide 4: Polvo interno — Calor atrae polvo, ciclo destructivo"}
